  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.flink.util.Visitable<org.apache.flink.api.common.operators.Operator<?>>

    public class FileDataSink
extends org.apache.flink.api.common.operators.base.FileDataSinkBase<org.apache.flink.types.Record>
    Operator for nodes which act as data sinks, storing the data they receive in a file instead of sending it to another contract. The encoding of the data in the file is handled by the FileOutputFormat.
    See Also:
    FileOutputFormat
